<ab facs="#facs_603_line_1592208460850_4558">iſt </ab>
</del></add><ab facs="#facs_603_line_1592208475696_4568">fürbraht worden . vvie man <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Augſtein bey ew </ab><ab facs="#facs_603_r1l26">beſchuldig 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd auf Jn <expan>auſʒgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab </del> daʒ Er 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnſer </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_603_line_1592208484418_4578">auff </ab></add> kunt </ab><ab facs="#facs_603_r1l30">ſchaft 
